niceDesc: Personal space that recreates the Primarch s Vigilarium from FINAL FANTASY XIII. 2009, 2010 SQUARE ENIX CO., LTD. All Rights Reserved. CHARACTER DESIGN  TETSUYA NOMURA
Author: s091448

niceDesc: Like cars. Like workshops. Want to live in a workshop full of cars. Then this PetrolHead apartment is the place for you...
Author: gburwinm

niceDesc: Take a stroll down memory lane, take a left at nostalgia avenue and you ll find yourself in the original Home Square.
Author: astone

niceDesc: Enjoy a penalty shoot-out against the worlds greatest robot goalkeeper on your very own tropical island at dusk. In addition to the SFRGBT.. minigame, the island comes complete with beach shelter, roaring fire and a boat to take you home again. The minigame also includes 4 unique reward items (sand castle, bucket and spade, Mr. Wilson face ball and shark fin wearable accessory) which can only be won by playing against robo-goalie in this exclusive Personal Space.
Author: schaney

niceDesc: Every story has two sides, every day has it s night and every soul has it s dark side. What would happen if these two sides were ever parted, if magic entered the roots of your soul and divided it into two. The curse hung in the air filling every corner of the castle. The splitting of a soul in two, one side to hold all that was good, great and beautiful, the other half to be filled with the darkness of evil, bitterness and hatred. Here everything is light, the feeling of hope and happiness is palpable. But this is Twingate Castle...
Author: Mike

niceDesc: The Hollyridge Estate is the perfect setting for an elegant winter soiree. This personal space features classic Victorian architecture and design and also features built-in decorating options which allow you to create a festive atmosphere without taking up any furniture slots. Includes customizable wallpaper, a snowball fight minigame and much more.
Author: JLee

niceDesc: Your very own casino right on the strip. Treat your friends to a night of fun and games. Here, you are your own casino boss. Whatever you say goes.
Author: Administrator

niceDesc: Reign over your own celestial paradise with the Palace of the Seven Winds. Exert your influence over the heavens themselves to alter time, break free of your earthly shackles and take to the skies, lounge in your own personal harem-style apartments, have wishes granted by your personal genie, unlock rewards and much more.
Author: sctaylor

niceDesc: Lounge like the gods as you sit atop the clouds in your very own Mt. Olympus. Take your rightful place on the throne, overlooking your impluvium (a water basin for you mortals). Take a stroll out back in your peristylium to catch some sun. Make sure to have one of your worshippers pull up your chariot for you when you leave. Reward your guests with a Mount Olympus Bolts (Male or Female), exclusive to the Mount Olympus personal space.
Author: jlee

niceDesc: GZ Burger, a hamburger shop neighboring a large lake, is all yours. The interior layout of the tables, chairs, etc. is up to your imagination. Create your own unique restaurant and invite your friends.
Author: JLee

niceDesc: This Personal Space Recreates A Backstreet Housing Complex In Edo, A Town Full Of Humanity. If You Have This Personal Space, You Can Use The Tenement House In The Lounge Oedo  Exterminating Mononoke As A Recovery Base.

niceDesc: It s wet out there.
Author: VEEMEE

niceDesc: Hail Fratos, may his spirit forever soar as freely as his temple in the sky.

niceDesc: This FREE apartment is brought to you by nDreams. Expand your complex by getting any or all of the additional rooms. In doing so, you won t only impress your friends with a great apartment but you will be rewarded for your efforts.

niceDesc: Miles from civilisation and hidden deep in a gorge, this long-lost Dam is the perfect hideout for every aspiring evil overlord. The dark interior and bare rock set the mood and the Piranha pool adds a suitable finishing touch.

niceDesc: Enter if you dare. This tormented manor is steeped in grim history, history that will not remain in the past. Explore this mysterious apartment, but beware of the dangers that lurk within. Can you solve the cryptic riddles and learn the horrible truths ingrained within the structure s living, breathing walls.
Author: sctaylor

niceDesc: Spend your holiday on a luxurious private beach. The clear blue sea, the white sandy beach, and the cottage on the ocean are all yours. With a friend, or with that special someone. Your holiday has just begun.

niceDesc: The luxurious and gorgeous silver tearoom.Among the trees one can see a sparkling silver figure, said to take your breath away. In this mountain region far removed from civilization, you can spend some time with a cup of tea, cut off from everyday life. * A present from GZ Gift
Author: maenami

niceDesc: Take time out and relax in the birthplace of culture and art, 15th Century Italy. Place your treasured possessions within a luxurious Venice apartment overlooking the famous canals.
Author: ppurdy

niceDesc: Carla s Coffee Shop is located in the heart of the City and is the perfect place to catch up with old friends. With street areas and the coffee shop to decorate you can make this apartment your own.

niceDesc: Make a virtual journey to the cradle of western civilization and visit the archipelago off Greece s mainland. Here you ll live in a lush apartment with spectacular views of the ocean and surrounding city. Ya ssou.
Author: PPurdy

niceName: My Secret Villa on a Blue Whale
niceDesc: Take a trip through the ocean on the back of a whale. Visit tropical countries, the Mediterranean, and even the northern fjords. It s up to you where you steer the gentle giant as you enjoy this relaxing cruise.

niceDesc: Now you can catch fish all day with the Go Fish Tropical Island. This private island gives you access to all the fishing you could ever want, along with your own beach to relax on.

niceName: Blaster s Paradise - Sodium Personal Space
niceDesc: Blast your way to an epic score with the awesome TankTop shooter in this stunning sub-tropical personal space. With spectacular waterfalls, a mysterious abandoned mill, and the addictive TankTop shooter, this waterside hang-out will be the envy of all your friends.
Author: ppurdy

niceDesc: Welcome to Chinatown - a cool new apartment space from nDreams. Hang out in Chinatown Square, or shelter from the rain in the surrounding building.
Author: CarlaR

niceDesc: Take time out from all the racing and partying to enjoy the festival from afar in your mesa-top campsite.
Author: stuart_barnett

niceDesc: Enjoy the summer in your new French Chateau. This stunning Chateau has a giant foyer and balcony, where you can bask in the light from your chandelier. But the real jewel is out back. Take a leisurely stroll in the courtyard, complete with perfectly manicured trees and bushes. All this natural beauty may inspire you to hang up some new art in your not so humble abode. Reward your guests with a French Chateau Painting, exclusive to the French Chateau personal space.
Author: jlee

niceDesc: These large private suites are normally reserved for high-ranking officers of the Earth Fleet. Civilians and pilots alike may now claim their own piece of the Novus Prime space station, at least until these suites run out. Space is available to install your own hangar for your fighter ships, which allows you to play missions with your guests. You may also install a Zero-gravity Simulation system, which allows occupants to safely float about the quarters.
Author: ppurdy

niceDesc: GZ Burger, a hamburger shop neighbouring a large lake, is all yours. The interior layout of the tables, chairs, etc. is up to your imagination. Create your own unique restaurant and invite your friends.

niceName: Hollywood Hills House Daytime Estate (with Home Theater)
niceDesc: Live like a celebrity with a mansion in the Hollywood Hills, set above the LA skyline. Invite your friends into your home theater for a social viewing experience with videos, trailers and exclusive content from Sony Pictures. Features include  Built-in Entertainment On Demand theater system A swimming feature for the infinity pool. THIS is the estate to own if you want to relax in the lap of luxury with your friends. Purchase of this estate comes bundled with the LOOT Active Camera and Active Light, so you can film your parties and upload them to YouTube at no extra cost. PLEASE READ  Due to contractual and rights agreements, all content may not be available in all countries. Content availability is dependent on the geolocation of the device. CRACKLE content is only available in US, CA, UK, and AU. RADIOIO is only available in US and CA. Only one LOOT TV or LOOT Radio can be active at a time.
Author: PPurdy

niceDesc: Hidden in a top secret location, this Vault is filled with a collection of new suits from Iron Fusion, each with their own individual mechanics. The Iron Fusion Vault holds the secrets to metering out swift justice in PlayStation Home. Upon entering the Iron Fusion Vault, the owner will be awarded Mechjet Glory plus four special suits  Panthabot Teigra, Mechjet Ferruma, Mechjet Ragnara and Mechsuit-Pilot Necra.
Author: JLee

niceDesc: The time has come to hit the road and party. Take full advantage of the freedoms a virtual world provides, slip the bus into cruise control and join the party at full speed. Just remember what goes on tour, stays on tour.
Author: Mike

niceDesc: Additional Personal Gardens In The Palais Region. More Gardening Plans Are Available, Giving You More Freedom To Plant Your Planters. The Images Are Gardening Examples.
Author: Sony Computer Entertainment

niceDesc: A relaxing atmosphere for body and soul. Invite a friend, take a soak together in the soothing waters, and watch the days fatigue melt away.
Author: nakazoe

niceDesc: Washed ashore on a solitary island in the south seas. The blazing sun, the quiet ocean, the refreshing breeze, crap. I built a house on top of a cliff and even forgot to go home. You are now able to go to the Southern Island Hideaway lounge from the back door of the loghouse. Also, there are plans to add many different things to this personal space in the future.

niceDesc: For a limited time only get the exclusive Chamber apartment for Home. This apartment blends the real and surreal with fire-pits, waterfalls, and even a mysterious giant tree in the center that seems to come alive when walking by.
Quadruple Room, No Bath, Shared Toilet. The Property Is Conveniently Located Near The Downtown Area.

niceDesc: Enjoy Gnome Curling in the privacy of your own secret garden. Comes complete with a gazebo, beautiful floral displays and a magical door to take you back home again.

niceDesc: The Space Station needs a crew, and you ve been selected to take part in an all new out-of-this-world experience. Your Space Station adventure will have you defending your new home against incoming asteroids in the fully interactive Station Defense turret center. On top of defending the station your tasks will also include lowering and raising the external shutters so you don t get blinded by the sun and you ll even have to evacuate the garbage you produce in to the vaccum of space. Your shuttle is cleared for arrival. The Space Station space is a clubhouse where everyone is invited to join.
Author: sctaylor

niceDesc: For centuries, Castle Strakh has been the subject of tales and superstition amongst the local people. Some say the castle is haunted by the ghostly bride of Count Strakh, others that it hides a secret lab used for horrific experiments. Do you dare seek out the truth. Contains 11 ghastly rewards and LKWD Life XP.
Author: Lockwood

niceDesc: Hidden deep within the forest, Creek Falls sits at the bed of a stunning waterfall. The home is built like a modern day studio with a living room and bedroom packed into one large open space. You can even hang out with friends in your outdoor patio and breathe in the soft chilly wind of the autumn air. Reward yourself and your friends with an exclusive Animated Autumn Tree furniture items, only available in Creek Falls.
Author: jlee

niceDesc: The nDreams Luxury Lighthouse apartment is spread across multiple floors and comes complete with authentic rotating light effect. Situated on a picturesque cliffside this is the perfect get away.

niceDesc: Take your living experience to new heights with the Tycoon Penthouse, perched high above the city sky. The window-walled space comes with your own private helipad, an aquarium that reaches from floor to ceiling, and a spiralling staircase that gives the space its modern design. Dare to defy gravity and add this little slice of heaven to your collection today.
Author: PPurdy

niceDesc: In this new apartment, you can take up arms in the training yard, entertain guests in the audience chamber, or survey your surroundings from the castle ramparts.

niceDesc: If we Zombies have offended, think but this, and all is mended, that you have but slumber d here, while these corpses did appear.

niceDesc: The Dream has become a Nightmare. This once opulent yacht has gone to wrack and ruin. Experience the eerie surroundings for yourself and discover some wicked rewards. Board this cursed vessel at your own peril, you have been warned
Author: JLee

Now this can be a virtual reality with our Snow Globe Clubhouse, set on a table inside The Jam Jar, the outside world is visible and giant. Live the magic and feel the snow because after all .. There s Snow Place like PlayStation Home.

Combine this with a large, glass-walled, infinity pool that looks out into the ocean s horizon and you have the perfect backyard for any social get-together or simply a relaxing afternoon. And for an added bonus the PlayStation Home Mansion also includes up to 5 unique gold rewards for each of your guests.

niceDesc: The Stately Home (Gothic) is the perfect Clubhouse for those people who like the finer things in life with a slightly darker twist. With its large and beautiful grounds and a direct link through to the Masquerade Ball - The Ballroom (Gothic) Clubhouse, this space is a must-have. Also comes with five free rewards.

niceDesc: This dappled glade is the ultimate chilled out place to relax and unwind surrounded by nature. It s the gift of tranquility.

niceDesc: Jump onto an Audi S1 Sledge and race down the mountainside against up to 5 other players, with a chance to win rewards.

niceDesc: Please enjoy your stay at Paradise Springs. Compliments of the manager.

The splitting of a soul in two, one side to hold all that was good, great and beautiful, the other half to be filled with the darkness of evil, bitterness and hatred. Whether you decide to return it to it s full boutique status, use it s exquisite detail as a backdrop for a gallery or as the venue of the latest fashion event, The Jam Jar will still prove to be THE place to be seen.

niceDesc: Unlock the mysteries of Cutteridge Estate. This elegant Victorian estate is rumored to be the final resting place of many dark and depraved souls. Do you dare to venture into these forsaken halls in search of the secrets which lie within.

niceDesc: This massive and fantastical outdoor apartment, situated on the side of a skyscraper overlooking a futuristic city, defies belief. Note  For only a small amount extra, purchase the Xi  Continuum - Axiom Agent Pack in the nDreams shop and obtain the game version of this apartment and access to Xi  Continuum, the exciting PlayStation Home adventure game featuring an evolving story, playable missions, and rewards.

niceName: LOOT s Sunset Yacht (With Home Theater)
niceDesc: Watch live events, videos, podcasts and exclusive content in your luxurious on-board theater while cruising along in a beautiful tropical lagoon. In addition, this upgraded Amaterasu yacht now offers the ability to set the mood of your cruise. Sunrise, sunset, day, night. It s your choice. Thrill to breathtaking views and host exclusive parties, or sit back and count the stars under the romantic moonlight.
Author: ppurdy

niceDesc: Admire the stunning sunset across a mountain lake from this modern log cabin. The residence provides two large living areas with beautiful fire places in each and exquisite lighting throughout. These are elegantly joined by a large decked area that takes you right up to the lake side. Simply spectacular.
Author: PlayStation Home

niceDesc: Personal apartment using the interior design of the throne room in Visari s palace.
Author: Guerrilla Games

niceDesc: Dance the night away in this stylish discotheque. Featuring animated disco balls, spotlights and lasers, this vast underground night-club even contains a rythm-action dance mini-game, with a high-score leaderboard. Getting a high score will give you an exclusive reward... Whether you prefer to challenge your friends at the mini-game, party on the animated illuminated dance floor, sit on the stools at the bar, or relax on the comfy armchairs, this is the perfect place to invite your friends.
Author: JLee

niceDesc: Your very own LittleBigPlanet Pod Penthouse. Pod is crafted from the finest cardboard and the view is simply out of this world.
Author: Stephen_Routledge

niceDesc: This luxurious multilevel suite overlooks the endless hustle and bustle of the Las Vegas strip. From million dollar views of Sin City s sprawling lights to extravagant amenities like the romantic rooftop hot tub, this magnificent residence is a must-have property for PlayStation Home high-rollers.
Author: jlee

niceDesc: Nestled atop a steep and perilous mountain Ajagara s Peak is only accessible to a select few - those known as the Dragon Scouts. A place for diligent training, scholarly pursuits and deep meditation the monastery at Ajagara s Peak was founded to train an elite band of soldiers who keep watch over the kingdom of Ajagara. With 7 daily rewards and the chance to catch a glimpse of a tame dragon, this truly is a unique personal space.
Author: Lockwood

niceDesc: Peakvox Ninja This Personal Space Is Based On A Japanese Style Lounge. Owners Of This Hermitage Will Always Receive A 50% Increase In Login Bonuses In This Lounge. Placing The Following Furniture Sets (or Just Possessing Them) Will Further Increase The Login Bonus 25% Additional...Purchasers Of Decorative Japanese Furniture Sets 25% Additional...Purchasers Of Partition Japanese Furniture Sets 20% Additional...Purchasers Of Garden Set (pine) 20% Additional...Purchasers Of Garden Set (bamboo) 30% Additional ...10% Additional For Purchasers Of Garden Stone Sets...10% Additional For Purchasers Of Coolness Set 1...10% Additional For Purchasers Of Coolness Set 2...10% Additional For Purchasers Of Coolness Set 3 Visits To The Peakvox Ninja Lounge And The Benefits Of The Benefits Are Available To Those Who Are 17 Years Of Age Or Older. This Personal Space Can Be Used As A Regular Personal Space By Those Under 17 Years Old.

niceDesc: The wonderous Avalon Keep is now an expansive Clubhouse. Invite your friends to enjoy this space with all the same features as the personal space. Any upgrades you purchase for the Avalon Keep will also be reflected in the Clubhouse and vice versa. The Avalon Keep is an impregnable fortress on your very own floating island. The magical crystals of Avalon allow the landmass to stay afloat and power all the new technological advances that have swept the world of Avalon. Your Keep sets you apart as one of the nobility that have taken residence in the skies around Avalon. Master all the mini-games and share the wealth with the latest in gift machine technology. Can you unlock all the secrets of your Keep. - Dragonfly Automaton - Gift Machine for owners and guests - Scavenger Hunts for owners and guests - Interactive NPCs - Crystal Hunter Mini-game - Diurnal Controls
Author: Stephen

niceDesc: This personal space is your very own tropical island inhabited by LocoRoco characters. The tropical retreat is full of exciting activities. Collect berries that fall from the trees, and communicate with islanders to expand the facilities. Enjoy the Swing, Slide, Jukebox, and games for two players. And the more time you spend on Loco Island, the more vibrant and exciting the paradise becomes. Treat yourself to this fun-filled personal space.

niceDesc: Joe s Boxing Gym is the perfect place to hang out if you want to work on your moves and learn how to spit sawdust.

niceDesc: Relax and get back to nature in this charming country farm. In this space you can raise plants and animals to improve your farming skills. As you gain experience, you will be able to plant new crops and raise new animals. Chop wood and level your woodworking skills to create furnishings for yourself or to gift to a guest. Place crafted furniture items in Bramblenook Farm for no furniture cost.

niceDesc: A Virtua Tennis Court Game. Stop the robots.

niceDesc: A secluded glade under a moonlit starry sky. Gather around the solitary tree and warm yourself by the glow of the fire. It s the perfect place for a fireworks party.

niceDesc: A personal space to enjoy the changing seasons.

niceDesc: Take a minute and unwind at the charming Desert Haven clubhouse. Catch a couple sun-rays poolside while socializing with friends or meeting new ones. Take a nap beneath the cabanas or even catch a fireside chat next to the bonfires. The Desert Haven space is a clubhouse where everyone is invited to join.

niceDesc: Experience life at a toy s eye view in Andy s room from Disney Pixar s Toy Story 3.

niceDesc: The Living Room Stage Set provides Home users the opportunity to shout lights, camera, action. while collaborating with their friends to bring their own movies and television shows to life. This includes 20 existing Gift Machine clothing items and 9 exclusive new clothing items.

niceDesc: This is the peakvox ninja personal space, Japanese lounge.

niceDesc: The best spot from which to embark upon your next swashbuckling adventure.. No matter the plunders you seek, you and your friends will have the time of your life. Check out the pirate ship, walk the plank, shadow dancing, play checkers, best your mateys at liar s dice, or furnish your space with all your ill-begotten gains. All this and an ocean view. Thee place to assemble before going off to play Cutthroats  Battle for Black Powder Cove .

niceDesc: Enjoy a bit of rest and relaxation in this modern two-story lake house complete with a kitchen, bedroom, and dock with your very own rowboat. In addition to that, the serene life-like atmosphere of dancing fire-flies and migrating birds will surely erase any motivation of returning to the busy city streets.

niceDesc: A radical nightclub space with all the essentials. Food in the fridge, tunes in the stereo and lots of space for multi-level dance floor action. State of the art everything. Four floors of fun in a hi-tech heaven that would make even the Great Gatsby jealous. If lavish is your lifestyle, then this is your new party pad.

niceDesc: An idyllic marina apartment perfect for spending the night before your next big adventure. Luxuriate in stylish surroundings with a stunning tropical sunset view, exotic wildlife and magnificent craft around you.

But no new piece of real estate would be complete without a wardrobe so included is Old West attire and furniture to truly give your new home an authentic look and feel. This Saloon is so jammed packed with items and minigames you ll be the talk of the town. The Old West Saloon space is a clubhouse where everyone is invited to join.

Indulge yourself in a classic game of pool or the darts mini-game that comes included in your new game lounge. As an added bonus, each section of the PlayStation Home Mansion includes up to 5 unique gold rewards for you and your guests.

Long ago this magical knowledge was lost and the towers and spires gradually fell into disrepair until only a few remained. Awaken the Genie, unleash his magic and reap the rewards. Flying Carpet Gem Collection Mini-game Interactive Genie Unlockable rewards and apartment customisations

niceDesc: A mansion isn t really a mansion without an expensive place to keep your rides. That s why we created an over-sized four-door garage to accompany the PlayStation Home Mansion. Your showroom comes equipped with overhead lights to help showoff your prized trophies. There is more to this fancy showroom that meets the eye can you find the missing pieces. As an added bonus, each section of the PlayStation Home Mansion includes up to 5 unique gold rewards for you and your guests.

All doors are automatic. Included is a built in sound system, games, plus rewards for the owner and guests. It truly has more features than can be listed here. It is a must see to believe.

niceDesc: Looking for a nice and tranquil place to stay. The Mahjong apartment is just the place. This walled apartment in an busy Orient city is an oasis of rest with blossom trees and koi carps. If you are looking for something more lively you can try the Mahjong Attack game that comes with the apartment. Mahjong Attack is a challenging variant of Mahjong Solitaire which is all about speed. You play the game alone (single player), together with your friends (co-op) or against your friends (multiplayer).
Author: schaney

niceDesc: The luxurious and gorgeous golden tearoom. Among the trees one can see its sparkling golden form, said to take your breath away. In this mountain region far removed from civilization, you can spend some time with a cup of tea, cut off from everyday life. * A gift from GZ gift
Author: maenami

niceName: The Dream Yacht  Arctic Voyage Clubhouse
niceDesc: Treat yourself to the sights of breathtaking glaciers, giant ice formations and crystal blue waters with the Dream Yacht  Arctic Voyage. Explore three decks, chill out on the private ice shelf and collect 8 unique rewards. Live the dream.
Author: Lockwood

niceDesc: The Bunker Bar is the ultimate live music venue. A dynamically lit stage dominates one side of the space with an ultra cool, chic bar and hangout to the other side. Party.
Author: Lockwood

niceDesc: This is the personal space for the more adventurous Home buyer. Space is limited, so act now.
Author: PPurdy

niceDesc: An understated residence for aspiring nobility to call their own. A perfect place to relax and hold out against the siege of life.
Author: GBBrislSi

niceDesc: TARDIS stands for Time And Relative Dimension In Space. The TARDIS looks like a 1950 s wooden Police Phone Box on the outside, but is of infinite proportions on the inside. Amaze your friends when they discover the wonder of Time Lord technology. Doctor Who logo 2013 and TM BBC. Licensed by BBC WW Ltd.
Author: JLee

niceDesc: The Neptune Suite offers a virtual life of luxury in this opulent underwater paradise. Enjoy this action-packed personal space featuring an 8-player picture scramble game, a 4-player action game, an interactive robotic pet, and a sweeping underwater glass wall vista. Buy now.
Author: PP

niceDesc: Relax and re-energise in the exotic and picturesque grounds of Paradise Health Club. Chill out by the pool, sunbathe on the terrace or detox in the sauna.
Author: CarlaR

niceDesc: Looking For A Nice And Tranquil Place To Stay. The Mahjong Apartment Is Just The Place. This Walled Apartment In An Busy Orient City Is An Oasis Of Rest With Blossom Trees And Koi Carps. If You Are Looking For Something More Lively You Can Try The Mahjong Attack Game That Comes With The Apartment. Mahjong Attack Is A Challenging Variant Of Mahjong Solitaire Which Is All About Speed. You Play The Game Alone (single Player), Together With Your Friends (co-op) Or Against Your Friends (multiplayer).
Author: Sony Computer Entertainment

niceDesc: Warm, humid, and exotic. For a small fee, you too can own a piece of Paradise.
Author: ppurdy

niceDesc: The Basic Clubhouse for you to customise as you wish.
Author: Mark Anderson

niceName: My Secret Villa on a Blue Whale
niceDesc: Take a trip through the ocean on the back of a whale. Visit tropical countries, the Mediterranean, and even the northern fjords. It s up to you where you steer the gentle giant as you enjoy this relaxing cruise.
Author: maenami

niceDesc: The LIVING Collection - The House. Remember... Fashion passes, style remains, LIVING is the key.
Author: Mike

niceDesc: The Stately Home (Gothic) is the perfect personal apartment space for those people who like the finer things in life with a slightly darker twist. With its large and beautiful grounds and a direct link through to the Masquerade Ball - The Ballroom (Gothic) , this space is a must-have. Also comes with five free rewards.
Author: BenE

niceDesc: Don t be a square on those summer nights and head down to the VEEMEE 50 s Diner to hand jive, grab some food and hang with friends.
Author: euan

niceDesc: Enjoy a penalty shoot-out against the worlds greatest robot goalkeeper on your very own tropical island at dusk. In addition to the SFRGBT.. minigame, the island comes complete with beach shelter, roaring fire and a boat to take you home again. The minigame also includes 4 unique reward items (sand castle, bucket and spade, SFRGBT.. face ball and shark fin wearable accessory) which can only be won by playing against robo-goalie in this exclusive Personal Space.
Author: jlee

niceDesc: Unlock the mysteries of Cutteridge Mansion. This elegant Victorian mansion is rumored to be the final resting place of many dark and depraved souls. Do you dare to venture into these forsaken halls in search of the secrets which lie within.
Author: jlee

niceDesc: This personal space re-creates the collective residences on the back streets in the humantiy-overflowing Edo period. If you own this personal space, you can use
Author: Granzella Inc.

niceDesc: The Avalon Keep is an impregnable fortress on your very own floating island. The magical crystals of Avalon allow the landmass to stay afloat and power all the new technological advances that have swept the world of Avalon. Your Keep sets you apart as one of the nobility that have taken residence in the skies around Avalon. Master all the mini-games and share the wealth with the latest in gift machine technology. Can you unlock all the secrets of your Keep.
Author: jlee

niceDesc: The Stately Home is the perfect personal apartment space for those people who like the finer things in life. With its large and beautiful grounds and a direct link through to the Masquerade Ball - The Ballroom , this space is a must-have. Also comes with five free rewards.
Author: BenE

niceDesc: S.V.E.R. Barracks - The S.V.E.R. barracks is your private getaway to remote Central Asia. It features a spectacular sunset view, so you can relax on your large balcony, clean your rifle and watch strike fighters fly through the sun kissed heavens.
Author: ppurdy

niceDesc: The perfect setting for all your doodling. The Lock-a-doodle Studio includes a built in Lock-a-doodle mini-game plus a Gallery to display all your finest Doodles created in-game.
Author: JLee

niceDesc: Experience life on the grid in this apartment from Tron Evolution.
Author: ppurdy

niceDesc: This Is A Personal Space Where You Can Have The South Island Of LocoRoco Characters All To Yourself. This Island Is Full Of Playfulness. You Can Add Facilities By Collecting Nuts From The Island And Communicating With The Inhabitants. There Are Swings, A Slide, A Jukebox, And Even A Game That Can Be Played By Two People. The More You Play, The More Lively And Fun Loco Island Will Become. Enjoy The Personal Space With A Lot Of Volume.
Author: Sony Computer Entertainment

niceDesc: The Hollyridge Estate is the perfect setting for an elegant winter soiree. This personal space features classic Victorian architecture and design and also features built-in decorating options which allow you to create a festive atmosphere without taking up any furniture slots. Includes customizable wallpaper, a snowball fight minigame and much more.
Author: JLee

niceDesc: Personal Space Of The Exercise Hall Type Which Trains A Martial Art. Seemingly, The Decoyed Game Is Lived And Attached.

An affordable apartment from nDreams. For some reason a piece of this planet has broken away and is now floating between the Earth and the Moon. With stunning views of both it could be a perfect getaway to chill out amongst the stars.
Author: JLee

niceDesc: A unique live music venue - up to four players can grab an instrument and jam compete against each other. Comes complete with the Dance music pack additional packs are available to purchase at the Musicality shop.
Author: nDreams Ltd.

niceDesc: Welcome to the Hidden Oak Retreat, a clubhouse retreat tucked away in the mountains. Get away from the hustle of city life and enjoy one of the two relaxing fireplaces. Look up and and you ll notice the clubhouse lit by chandeliers made of antlers. Head out to the deck and enjoy the lakefront view while you roast some marshmallows on the campfire. Now this is the great outdoors. The Hidden Oak Retreat space is a clubhouse where everyone is invited to join.
Author: jlee

niceDesc: Enjoy a penalty shoot-out against the worlds greatest robot goalkeeper on your very own tropical island at dusk. In addition to the SFRGBT.. minigame, the island comes complete with beach shelter, roaring fire and a boat to take you home again. The minigame also includes 4 unique reward items (sand castle, bucket and spade, Mr. Wilson face ball and shark fin wearable accessory) which can only be won by playing against robo-goalie in this exclusive Personal Space.
Author: astone

niceDesc: The Space Station needs a crew, and you ve been selected to take part in an all new out-of-this-world experience. Your Space Station adventure will have you defending your new home against incoming asteroids in the fully interactive Station Defense turret center. On top of defending the station your tasks will also include lowering and raising the external shutters so you don t get blinded by the sun and you ll even have to evacuate the garbage you produce in to the vaccum of space. Also included with the Space Station is a chair, sofa, custom space helmet and a zero gravity UFO companion object to follow you all around PlayStation Home. Your shuttle is cleared for launch, awaiting your clearance.
Author: jlee

niceDesc: This personal space is your very own tropical island inhabited by LocoRoco characters. The tropical retreat is full of exciting activities. Collect nuts that fall from the trees, and communicate with islanders to expand the facilities. Enjoy the Swing, Slide, Jukebox, and games for two players. And the more time you spend on LocoIsland, the more vibrant and exciting the paradise becomes. Treat yourself to this fun-filled personal space.
Author: Sony Computer Entertainmnet

niceDesc: Moored by a tropical island, this ship comes complete with playable cannon mini-game and four Pirate themed furniture rewards. A very desirable residence that has suddenly become available, due to the imprisonment of the previous owner.
Author: stuart_barnett

niceDesc: You have been cordially invited to be a member of the Drey VIP Room. Take an exclusive look into the inspired fashions of Drey s celebrated designers. The Drey VIP Room features a stunning collection of old and new - everything to satisfy the hunger of the fashion elite worldwide. This includes 22 existing Gift Machine clothing items and 12 exclusive new clothing items.
Author: Lockwood

niceDesc: Spend some time beneath the waves in your own submarine, The Pearl Diver. Designed for combing through the sea floor, this underwater vessel is enclosed by glass to allow you to fully enjoy the aquatic sea life. The Pearl Diver space is a clubhouse where everyone is invited to join.
Author: staylor

niceDesc: The Modular Stage Set takes professional machinima to the next level. It provides the user with unprecedented levels of control over the floor, walls, backdrops, lights and camera systems. Also included are the Portable Camera and Portable Light active items, which let you take the LOOT machinima tools to any private space you own, transforming it into a perfect location for shooting your movies and TV shows. It is the ultimate tool for having fun with your friends while bringing new stories to life.
Author: LOOT

niceDesc: In this new clubhouse, you can take up arms in the training yard, entertain guests in the audience chamber, or survey your surroundings from the castle ramparts.
Author: KristianF

niceDesc: Make the first floor of a school building yours, including two classrooms, a shop, and a hallway. The layout of desks, chairs, and other items is up to you. Make your own unique classroom and enjoy school life along with your friends. Be careful not to stay at school until late at night. You never know what might happen...
Author: Granzella Inc.

niceDesc: LeChuck s Pirate ship. Sail the seven seas and even more with the new underground Lava transport hull. Strike fear in the hearts of Sailors and wannabe pirates. The sails may look ripped but they are still fully functional. Avast. And good luck.
Author: PPurdy

niceDesc: Jump on your snowmobile and explore the tundra in this exciting new personal space from Lockwood. From your modern apartment, you ll be able to look out onto the beautiful arctic surroundings before riding out to see what you can find. Includes Snowmobile Exploration minigame which allows you to cruise around the landscape, perform stunts and find 9 exclusive PlayStation Home rewards.
Author: Lockwood

niceDesc: Docked at Greek s famous Santorini harbor, your yacht is equipped with all the modern virtual conveniences you would expect. Step out on deck to take in the spectacular view or stay inside and relax with some friends.
Author: PPurdy

niceDesc: Miles from civilization and hidden deep in a gorge, this long-lost Dam is the perfect hideout for every aspiring evil overlord. The dark interior and bare rock set the mood and the Piranha pool adds a suitable finishing touch.
Author: ppurdy

niceDesc: Whether you prefer to chill out by the fountain, or dance with your friends in the music pavilion, there is always a good reason to come and visit this peaceful art-d co public park. Contains a go-kart racing game, a rythm-action game, and the Space Crash arcade cabinet. Playing the games will get you rewards.
Author: Tanguy

niceDesc: Prehistoric Valley is your regular lush mountaintop peaceful idyll it just happens to be around 100 million years ago and inhabited by cave people, dinosaurs, and giant mammals.
Author: JLee

niceDesc: The luxurious and gorgeous aqua tearoom.Among the trees one can see a sparkling aqua figure, said to take your breath away. In this mountain region far removed from civilization, you can spend some time with a cup of tea, cut off from everyday life. * A present from GZ Gift
Author: maenami
